189
00:10:09,445 --> 00:10:12,150
rahmat akan diagihkan pada raksasa-raksasa di sini.

190
00:10:13,267 --> 00:10:14,686
Rimuru-sama...

191
00:10:17,203 --> 00:10:18,509
Bersiap sedia semua!

192
00:10:18,843 --> 00:10:20,697
Ini adalah kemenangan kita.

193
00:10:20,697 --> 00:10:23,550
Seterusnya, giliran kita pula yang bekerja keras!

194
00:10:34,814 --> 00:10:35,935
Rimuru-sama!

195
00:10:35,935 --> 00:10:37,338
Tolong ambil tuan ni.

196
