Ambil jubah untuk dia.

197
00:10:39,634 --> 00:10:42,253
Ketahanannya pada haba mungkin tak berfungsi.

198
00:10:42,253 --> 00:10:43,022
Baik.

199
00:10:43,022 --> 00:10:44,728
Saya gembira awak selamat.

200
00:10:58,062 --> 00:10:59,053
Rimuru-sama...

201
00:10:59,498 --> 00:11:01,279
Disebabkan kau dah jadi Raja Syaitan,

202
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:04,519
aku harap kau tak mula menggila seperti orang lain.

203
00:11:06,489 --> 00:11:07,373
Notis.

204
00:11:07,911 --> 00:11:10,208
Festival Menuai telah pun bermula.

205
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,753
Komposisi badan dibentuk semula bagi...

206
