338
00:19:34,021 --> 00:19:35,172
Raja Syaitan...

339
00:19:35,172 --> 00:19:36,570
Dia dah berjaya ke?

340
00:19:40,810 --> 00:19:41,830
Notis.

341
00:19:42,780 --> 00:19:44,901
Di atas nama Raphael,

342
00:19:45,567 --> 00:19:49,821
memulakan kuasa Beelzebub bagi
menelan seluruh molekul magis...

343
00:19:50,379 --> 00:19:52,893
...dan jiwa yang ada di dalam penghadang ini.

344
00:20:09,766 --> 00:20:11,379
Saya dapat rasakan molekul magis...

345
00:20:11,379 --> 00:20:12,702
